reviewText: I'm giving this a one star rating not on the movie, but for the reason that i didn't know that this movie was only in German & not english as well. It's also is not for all regions either. It would of been nice to of had a heads up before i recieved this. I'm just letting anyone know ahead of time to be careful. I have seen this movie before & it's an asweome B-Movie. Just make sure you get the American copy lol.
